>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">T=</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;\\( z_1 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( z_2 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;\\( z_3 \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( x_1 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"2\">\\( \\begin{bmatrix} .5 &amp; .7 &amp; .5 \\\\ .9 &amp; .6 &amp; .5 \\end{bmatrix} \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( x_2 \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"width:250px; border-spacing: 1px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">C.</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">T=</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;\\( z_1 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;\\( z_2 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; \\( z_3 \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( x_1 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"2\">\\( \\begin{bmatrix} 0.7 &amp; 0.6 &amp; 0.5 \\\\ 0.8 &amp; 0.6 &amp; 0.4 \\end{bmatrix} \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( x_2 \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"width:250px; border-spacing: 1px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">D.</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\">T=</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;\\( z_1 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; &nbsp;\\( z_2 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td>&nbsp; \\( z_3 \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( x_1 \\)</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\" rowspan=\"2\">\\( \\begin{bmatrix} 0.7 &amp; 0.6 &amp; 0.5 \\\\ 0.8 &amp; 0.8 &amp; 0.8 \\end{bmatrix} \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\\( x_2 \\)</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table></div><br><br><b>Others: UGC NET CSE | July 2016 | Part 3 | Question: 64</b></p>",
